cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on the application of deep learning in computer vision, specifically in the area of single-image super-resolution. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the vulnerability of deep super-resolution methods to adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of security and privacy (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning models, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents experimental results and analysis, which could also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
